HEADWORD: Polyactinia
<hw>Pol`y*ac*tin"i*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.
See <er>Poly-</er>, and <er>Actinia</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
